&lt;h3 id=&#34;engineering-ethics--narrative&#34;&gt;Engineering Ethics &amp;amp; Narrative&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To introduce these concepts to students, we utilise a series of case studies and visual narratives. These stories highlight the &amp;ldquo;Accountability Gap&amp;rdquo; and the long-term career risks of &amp;ldquo;Cognitive Offloading.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
