&lt;h2 id=&#34;research--teaching-impact&#34;&gt;Research &amp;amp; Teaching Impact&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Currently deployed in &lt;strong&gt;ELEC1005 (Introduction to Software Engineering)&lt;/strong&gt;, this tool provides the telemetry needed for longitudinal studies on student personas and learning trajectories in the age of AI.&lt;/p&gt;



  
  &lt;blockquote class=&#34;border-l-4 border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-600 pl-4 italic text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 my-6&#34;&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;The goal is to move students from being &amp;lsquo;Passive Consumers&amp;rsquo; of AI to &amp;lsquo;Proactive Regulators&amp;rsquo; of the technology they deploy.&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;/blockquote&gt;

